              "x": "In advanced driving courses, participants learn how trail braking can enhance both safety and performance on challenging roads."
            },
            {
              "cf": "",
              "x": "When approaching a tight bend, professional drivers rely on trail braking to smoothly decelerate while maintaining momentum through the turn."
